  fiber: 4 g
  sodium: 1730 mg
servings: 2
time required: 20 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/honey-mandarin-chicken-and-pepper-stir-fry-6706c43466150a260f49b363
author: HelloFresh
